Share with:
Business Consultant Job (Information Technology) Jakarta, Indonesia
Country:
Indonesia
Function:
I.T.
Industry:
I.T.
Position type:
Permanent
Salary:
Negotiable
Created:
05 May 2014
Our client is the top online-retailer in Indonesia, created by one of the largest iconic shareholding group in e-commerce with a strong multinational presence. They deliver customers an easy access to purchase all types of products that are involved in electronics, home décor up until products from health-care to beauty just within a click of a button. This popular shopping platform are now seeking a highly – skilled professional in business consulting who can lead a direction and strategy for the company’s growth. Our highly respected client is seeking a graduate with a minimal of 3 years’ of committed experience from a top-notched consulting firm to fill the job of Business Consultant, to be based in Jakarta, Indonesia.
Main responsibilities:
To give a consultative approach to reach the objective of the project, suggesting improvements for implementation, what should be fixed and the best strategy to pursue and execute. This may include the reviewing of financial statements, evaluating competitors, and analyzing business practices. Once research is complete, business consultants may develop a new business model or prepare the recommendations for the project and company direction.
Requirements:
Min. bachelors (s1) in Business or related field
Has a min. of 3 years of experience in business consultancy from a highly reputable multinational consulting firm
MBA preferable
Dynamic, innovative and a detail-oriented individual
A natural strong ethical business sense
All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence.